# ft_irc

![C++]
![Network Programming]
![42 Project]
![Status]

A C++ Internet Relay Chat server built as part of the 42 Network curriculum.

`ft_irc` is a lightweight IRC server that supports multiple clients, authentication, channels, private messaging, and basic channel moderation. The project focuses on socket programming, non-blocking I/O, command parsing, and server-side client management.

